mixin b-intro()
    .b-intro
        picture(class="b-intro-image-wrap")
            source(class="b-intro-image" type="image/webp" srcset="../../img/content/mobile/1-intro/1/1-1x.webp 1x, ../../img/content/mobile/1-intro/1/1-2x.webp 2x," media="(max-width: 375px)")
            source(class="b-intro-image" type="image/jpeg" srcset="../../img/content/mobile/1-intro/1/1-1x.jpg 1x, ../../img/content/mobile/1-intro/1/1-2x.jpg 2x" media="(max-width: 375px)")
            source(class="b-intro-image" type="image/webp" srcset="../../img/content/tablet/1-intro/1/1-1x.webp 1x, ../../img/content/tablet/1-intro/1/1-2x.webp 2x," media="(max-width: 767px)")
            source(class="b-intro-image" type="image/jpeg" srcset="../../img/content/tablet/1-intro/1/1-2x.jpg 1x, ../../img/content/tablet/1-intro/1/1-2x.jpg 2x" media="(max-width: 767px)")
            img(class="b-intro-image" alt="intro-door" src="../../img/content/mobile/1-intro/1/1-1x.jpg")
        .b-container.b-container--no-padd-desktop
            h1(class="b-title b-title-intro") Stylish doors
            div(class="b-subtitle b-subtitle-intro") сделанные по&nbsp;новейшим разработкам&nbsp;из проверенных материалов